title: Scratchtastic Old Skool Mix 5 - DJ Kippax
description:
Here&#039;s a brand new old skool mix i made in March 2008. Due to popularity of the last one i thought id best make another.

Mix is approx 170meg in size recorded at 350k/bits mp3 using Lame 3.97.

   9.Alcatraz ? Give me Love
  10.More Kante ? Yeke Yeke
  11.Outlander ? Vamp

If you like what you hear please feel free to checkout my site www.djkippax.com. which contains more of my mixes which are all free to download.
If you want to keep updated on when i create any new mixes, gig dates, etc join my mailing list via my sites frontpage.

All the best and enjoy the mix.
James
(dj kippax)
